Several people feared dead and many others sustained injuries yesterday shortly after flag-off of the governorship campaign rally of the PDP in Pankshin the Central Senatorial zone of Plateau State when a truck conveying party supporters had an accident close to the Panyam Bridge. Sources from the community told LEADERSHIP Sunday that the incident happened at about 4 30 p.m.
Efforts to reach relevant authorities to get the full details at the time of sending this report were not successful.